se_url)\n  File \"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/scripts/generate_quiz.py\", line 64, in get_llm_client\n    raise ValueError(\"Ark API key required. Set ARK_API_KEY env var or use --api-key\")\nValueError: Ark API key required. Set ARK_API_KEY env var or use --api-key\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775024442864}}
