{"type":"message","id":"c5837f6a","parentId":"f8bfd9e6","timestamp":"2026-04-03T01:49:15.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 🎉 OpenClaw 每日资讯 - 2026年4月3日\n\n## 最新发布：OpenClaw v2026.4.2 正式上线\n\n昨天 OpenClaw 发布了最新版本 v2026.4.2，主要更新：\n\n### 破坏性变更\n- xAI 和 web_fetch 配置路径迁移，运行 `openclaw doctor --fix` 自动迁移\n\n### 新增功能\n- 恢复 Task Flow 基础设施，支持持久化后台编排\n- 新增 Android Google Assistant 入口\n- 支持飞书文档评论事件流\n\n### 问题修复\n- 修复了配对认证、推送通知、流式传输等多个问题\n\n[查看详情下载](https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/releases/tag/v2026.4.2)\n\n完整文章已保存到 wechat_articles 目录。"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775180955594}}
